A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Counties – Construction of Sidewalks and Crosswalks – Safe Alternative Routes
3 to Public Schools
4 FOR the purpose of requiring a county board of education each year to prepare and post in
5 a certain manner a report that identifies pathways that public school students may
6 use to travel to school using only safe alternative routes under certain circumstances;
7 requiring the governing body of a county each year to review a certain report and
8 construct any sidewalks and crosswalks necessary to create safe alternative routes
9 for public school students under certain circumstances; requiring the governing body
10 of a county to develop a certain plan with a certain governmental entity or person
11 and make certain efforts to execute the plan under certain circumstances; and
12 generally relating to safe alternative routes to public schools.
